  • Method Details

    • setNextState

      protected void setNextState()
      Sets the next state based on the following algorithm:

      Differentiation between setup phase and turn phase -> check isSetupDone to know which phase to limit the choice to If the setup phase is not concluded: -> check whether the leader setup still needs to be done, else go to the resource setup, which will internally choose whether it still needs to be done or whether it has to simply show the waiting screen If the setup phase is concluded: -> check whether the current player and the local player are the same player and switch accordingly
